    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Meals eaten out of doors, especially when part of an excursion to the countryside, coast, or other outdoor location. Originally, a meal for which each guest contributed a share of the food; this may be true of contemporary picnics, but is not necessarily so.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
